==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Collier
<hw>Col"lier</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>colier</ets>. See <er>Coal</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
engaged in the business of digging mineral coal or making charcoal, or
in transporting or dealing in coal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A vessel employed in the coal trade.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colliery</ent>⟦br⟧
